On january 24, 2010
Zephides
Since so many people want to make their own thread when looking for a clan, I decided (after a tip) to make this sticky thread.

Here you can put your own requests, where Clan leaders can look through if they need a new member.

A few tips:
1) A clan often has a few requirements, such as a certain amount of points, levels or gatherabilities. Let them know what you can do.
2) Some clans are looking for people from a specific country (due to the language that is spoken in their clan).
3) There are clans who want to participate in wars and others don't. What do you want?
4) The clans often have their own reqruitement topic. See if they need a few more members.

Goodluck to all who are looking for a clan!

Remember, this is an English version of DinoRPG. We'd like to see English only in the public forums.

I want to ask everyone to not promote your clan here. You already have your own recruitement thread. If not, create one for your clan.

I don't want this thread to be overwhelmed by clanpromotions. The posts from people who are actually requesting might get lost that way.

Thank you .
